| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6528 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonforce)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2e566a0c-0bd2-5b09-ba11-330949865987"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
